at the media displays--for as you can glean from my descriptions above, we are in combat, quiet and constant against a determined foe. A foe who wants far more than his products are worth."), mdx("p", null, "At any rate, I miss home. I cannot wait to return there again. Stay safe, for danger abounds everywhere."), mdx("p", null, "Humbly yours."));
