d little boys playing hide and seek in the world\u2019s greatest playground."), mdx("p", null, "I could describe the rubble for days; but I\u2019ll share the pictures instead, once they\u2019ve been developed. After touring the city, I walked to the market, an experience, for which I was completely unprepared."), mdx("p", null, "Guidelines for surviving a real, Arabic marketplace:"), mdx("ol", null, mdx("li", {
