  }), "self-consciousness in puberty"), ". Introductions are intractably, irreversibly bad. Bad in the sense that the things that you say about people you respect behind their backs are bad. Bad the way that eating pickles when you\u2019re expecting donuts is bad. Bad. I met my father, and it was bad. Bad in the ", mdx("a", _extends({
